# Plan: Goal-Transaction Sync & User-Defined Deadlines

Integrate the "Saving Goals" feature deeper into the core finance ledger so that every "Save" action is a traceable transaction.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Refined Deduction Logic:**
> - When you **Add Funds** via the Goals screen, I will create an **EXPENSE** transaction. This will deduct the amount from your total balance and show up in your "History".
> - I will use the category **"Savings"** for these transactions by default. Does that work for you?

