## Proposed Changes

### 1. Data Layer (Ledger Sync)

#### [MODIFY] [FinanceRepository.kt](file:///c:/Users/NTS/Documents/Finance_manager/app/src/main/java/com/nts/financemanager/data/repository/FinanceRepository.kt)
Update `insertTransactionWithGoalUpdate` to:
- Increment `savedAmount` for both `INCOME` and `EXPENSE` when a `goalId` is present.
- (An `EXPENSE` with a `goalId` represents "moving" money into that goal).

### 2. ViewModel Logic

#### [MODIFY] [GoalsViewModel.kt](file:///c:/Users/NTS/Documents/Finance_manager/app/src/main/java/com/nts/financemanager/ui/goals/GoalsViewModel.kt)
